short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Chromium Extension to check for Phishing websites from the URL.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This Add-on can be used to check if the website you are browsing is malicious or not. It employs advanced machine learning techniques that uses as much as 10 different features from the URL to detect malicious websites. This Add-on doesn't read or use any text, image or other contents from the website for the detection.
